MODIFICATIONS:

Version 2.0 (2025) - Dave Friedel / Wisetail
- Replaced arc4random() with SecRandomCopyBytes for secure random generation
- Added memory cleanup for sensitive data
- Implemented constant-time string comparison to prevent timing attacks
- Added modern Swift error handling with BCryptError enum
- Created BCryptSwiftModern struct with modern Swift patterns
- Added BCryptConfiguration for structured configuration
- Added async/await support for iOS 13+
- Added comprehensive test suites
- Added Swift Package Manager support
- Fixed division by zero vulnerability
- Maintained backward compatibility with legacy API